Im also looking for guys that could give me ideas to make the server better, coz im just out of ideas lol.
[b]Contact:[/b] Skype:blessed.city Msn: Dutchreality317@hotmail.com
[b][size=14pt]Team For Now[/size][/b]
[b]Java Programmers (Server Sided):[/b] [1/3] - Me (Mostly the basics) - Cedric - OPEN
[b]Java Programmers (Client Sided)[/b] [1/2] - Nami - OPEN
[b]Graphic Designers[/b] [1/2] - Me - Mees

[b]Beta Testers[/b] [0/50]
[b]We're looking for some1 to host this.[/b]
